-            Argument to be valid.  The default of 0 implies that the argument 
-            is optional.
-          </td>
-        </tr>
-        <tr>
-          <td>maximum</td>
-          <td>int</td>
-          <td>
-            The maximum number of values that can appear in a valid command 
-            line.  A value less than minimum is not allowed.
-          </td>
-        </tr>
-        <tr>
-          <td>consumeRemaining</td>
-          <td>String</td>
-          <td>
