-          is less than or greater than a specific number.  The lower bound is set using 
-          the <code>setMinimum( Number )</code>, and the upper bound is set using
-          the <code>setMaximum( Number )</code>.
-        </p>
-      </subsection>
-      
-      <subsection name="UrlValidator">
